<keyLead box="[136,1451,500,522]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">4 Context yellowish to pale yellow when mature; stipe club-shaped or sub-cylindrical .....................................................................5</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[136,1451,240,759]" box="[136,1450,528,550]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">
<keyLead box="[136,1450,528,550]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">
4 Context whitish to white when mature; stipe usually strongly bulbously swollen at the base .......................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[1351,1450,529,550]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Boletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="satanas">
<emphasis box="[1351,1450,529,550]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">R. satanas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
